K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:122b-1: a'arya aaksha ya ma ti ni rde sha n'a ma mah'a y'a na s'utra /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:123b-7: spyod lam mdzes pa phun sum tshogs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:123b-8: sbyin pa'i gnas chen por gyur pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:123b-10: byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun chen po dang yang thabs gcig ste /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:123b-24: sangs rgyas kyi chos mnyan pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:123b-25: yongs su tshol bas mi ngoms pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:124a-0: rtag tu rgyun mi 'chad par sems can thams cad yongs su smin par bya ba la brtson pa thabs @124a *//

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:124a-15: byang chub sems dpa' rnam par blta ba'i mig dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:124a-16: byang chub sems dpa' mun pa dang bral ba dang; byang chub sems dpa' byams pa dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:124b-21: thogs pa med pa'i ye shes kyi byin gyi rlabs kyi sgor 'jug pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:125a-0: chos thams cad ji lta ba bzhin @125a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:125a-1: du shin tu gtan la bab par bstan pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:125a-16: sems rab tu dben pa shes pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:125a-17: theg pa chen pos gdul ba'i phyir thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi sar dbang bskur ba thob pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:125a-25: rnam par rig par mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:125a-26: rab tu shes par mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:125a-30: gsal bar mdzad do; ;yang dag par rab tu ston to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:125b-0: de nas bcom ldan 'das de lta bu shin tu rnam par nges pa'i don 'dus pa chen po'i le'u'i chos kyi rnam grangs 'di rgya cher yang dag par rab @125b tu ston pa na /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:125b-32: nags tshal rnams sgrib par mi byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:126a-6: ri btang zung chen po'ang rung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:126a-7: ri'i rgyal po chen po thams cad kyang sgrib par mi byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:126a-8: ma nar med pa'i sems can dmyal ba chen po yan chad thams cad du thal te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:126a-15: rin po che bkod pa'i 'khor gyi khyams su bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor gyi khor yug thams cad du rin po che sna bdun gyi padma kha tshon shing rta'i phang lo tsam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:126a-16: 'dab ma bye ba brgya stong du ma dang ldan pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:126b-0: rin po che'i padma de dag re re las dri gang byung ba'i @126b dri des stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kun tu rgyas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:126b-1: gang stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di'i lha dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:126b-21: padma bkod pa sngon ma mthong ma thos pa 'di dag byung ba su'i snga ltas lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:126b-22: de skad ces gsol pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:126b-23: bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:126b-25: 'di ni shar phyogs nas byang chub sems dpa' blo gros mi zad pa zhes bya ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127a-0: byang chub sems dpa' bye ba phrag @127a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127a-1: drug cus yongs su bskor zhing mdun du bdar nas lhan cig tu 'ong ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127a-2: de dag 'ong ba'i snga ltas so //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127a-8: glu rab tu len cing byang chub sems dpa' bye ba phrag drug cus yongs su bskor te mdun du bdar nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127a-9: lhan cig tu rin po che bkod pa'i 'khor gyi khyams ga la ba der bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der 'ongs te lhags nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127a-10: bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar steng gi bar snang la ta la bdun srid na 'khod nas thal mo sbyar te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127a-11: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di thams cad dbyangs kyis go bar byed cing /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127a-12: bcom ldan 'das la tshul dang 'dra ba'i tshigs su bcad pa 'di dag gis mngon par bstod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127a-13: rdul med rdul dang bral ba dpa' bo 'dod chags bral //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127a-14: ye shes rab rib mi mnga' spyan gsum rnam par sbyangs //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127a-15: skyon rnams bsal ba dri ma gsum dang tha ba spangs //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127b-0: rdul bral sangs rgyas thugs rje can la phyag @127b 'tshal lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127b-1: 'jigs dang bral zhing gti mug dra ba rnam par bsal //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127b-2: stobs bcu rgol ba'i tshogs kyis shin tu thul bar dka'//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127b-3: log pa'i lam zhugs pha rol tshogs skrag mdzad //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127b-4: seng ge lta bur bsnyengs pa mi mnga' sa la gshegs //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:127b-12: sman pa bzhin du rab tu grol bar mdzad cing gshegs //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:198b-10: tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:198b-11: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:198b-12: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:198b-13: bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:198b-14: 'di ni byang chub sems dpa'i 'dus byas la mkhas pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:198b-15: gang yang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'dus ma byas kyi ye shes kyi pha rol tu phyin pa lnga po dag la mi smod cing /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:198b-16: pha rol tu phyin pa thams cad kyi tshogs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:198b-17: dge ba'i rtsa ba bsags pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpa'i rnam par grol ba zag pa med pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:198b-18: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid du yongs su bsngo ba 'di ni de'i 'dus ma byas la mkhas pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:198b-20: 'dus byas la mkhas pa ni gang sems can thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i 'od zer mnyam par gtong ba'i phyir bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhis sems can sdud pa 'di ni byang chub sems dpa'i 'dus byas la mkhas pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:198b-21: gang yang sems can med pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199a-1: pas mi 'dzin mi len mchog tu 'dzin par mi byed cing /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199a-2: bsdu ba'i dngos po la mkhas pa de'ang 'dus ma byas la mos pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid du yongs su bsngo ba 'di ni de'i 'dus ma byas la mkhas pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199a-4: 'dus byas la mkhas pa ni gang 'khor ba'i rgyun gyi nyon mongs pa rnams gcod pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199a-5: 'khor ba'i rgyun gyi dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams mi gcod pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199a-6: byang chub sgrub pa'i kun tu sbyor ba rnams kyi rgyun 'brel pa nyi tshe ba'i kun tu sbyor ba rnams kun tu mi spyad pa 'di ni 'dus byas la mkhas pa zhes bya'o; ;gang yang stong pa nyid dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199a-8: smon pa med pa'i chos rnams la 'dris par byed pa'i ye shes rtog pa la mkhas pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199a-9: byang chub gzhan gyi dring la mi 'jog cing 'dus ma byas kyang mngon sum du mi byed pa 'di ni de'i 'dus ma byas la mkhas pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199a-11: 'dus byas la mkhas pa ni gang khams gsum la'ang spyod la; khams gsum na spyod pa'i nyon mongs pa rnams kyis kyang mi gos pa 'di ni de'i 'dus byas la mkhas pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199a-13: khams gsum nas nges par 'byung ba'i ye shes rab tu shes kyang nges par 'byung ba'i dbyings su'ang mi ltung ba 'di ni de'i 'dus ma byas la mkhas pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-0: gang chos thams cad la mkhas pa zhes smras pa de ni thams cad mkhyen @199b pa'i tshig bla dvags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-4: shes rab la mkhas pas thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes tshad med cing mi chags pa yongs su rdzogs par byed pa'i phyir te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-5: de'i phyir chos thams cad la mkhas pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-6: btsun pa sh'a radva ti'i bu /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-7: mkhas pa brgyad po de dag gis zin pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi shes rab mi zad pa yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-10: mi dge ba'i chos rnams rab tu shes pa ni shes rab bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-11: nges par 'byed pa'i cha dang mthun pa'i chos rnams la rtog pa ni shes rab bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-12: 'phags pa'i chos mngon par gyur pas na shes rab ni tshad mar gyur pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-13: shes rab ni lta bar gyur pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-16: chod pa thams cad yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du rab tu rtogs pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-19: smon pa thams cad kyi smon lam dang bral ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-20: shes rab ni nyon mongs pa'i yongs su gdung ba thams cad 'jil bas na sim par byed pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-21: shes rab ni chos kyi kun dga' la dga' ba'i rgyun ma chad pas na mchog tu dga' bar byed pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-22: shes rab ni don shes pa mngon sum du gyur pas rton pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-23: shes rab ni byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun po dag gi rten to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:199b-24: shes rab ni theg pa ji lta ba bzhin du 'bras bu thob par gyur pas na thob pa'i mtshan nyid do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-1: rab ni rang bzhin gyis ye shes snang bas na rab tu shes pa'i mtshan nyid do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-2: shes rab ni chu bo thams cad las sgrol bas na yang dag par rab tu sgrol ba'o; ;shes rab ni yang dag par skyon med par 'dren pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-3: shes rab ni dge ba'i chos thams cad rab tu sdud pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-4: shes rab ni sngon gyi nyon mongs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-5: bag la nyal thams cad dang bar byed pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-6: shes rab ni rtse mor gyur pa'i shes rab kyi mchog go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-7: shes rab ni rang byung gi ye shes rtogs pa'i phyir gya nom pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-8: shes rab ni khams gsum pa thams cad dang ma 'dres pa'i phyir rgyu dang bral ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-9: shes rab ni thabs kun gyis zin pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-10: shes rab ni 'phags pa thams cad kyis yongs su bzung ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-11: shes rab ni mtshan ma dang; yongs su rtog pa thams cad dang bral ba'i phyir tshad gzung du med pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-12: shes rab ni ma rig pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-13: gti mug gi mun pa thams cad ngang bral bas na bag med pa'i gnyen po'o; ;shes rab ni rnal 'byor spyod pa'i sa la gnas pa thams cad kyi sbyor ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-14: shes rab ni theg pa thams cad la yang dag par zhugs pa rnams kyi 'dren pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-15: shes rab ni ma rig pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200a-16: gti mug gi mun pa dang rab ring kyi ling tog sel bar byed pa'i phyir snang bar byed pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-0: shes rab ni mig la ji ltar mos pa rnams la mig thams cad @200b spyin par byed pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-2: gzugs kyi lam las yang dag par 'das pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-3: de bzhin du rna ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-12: chos kyi lam las yang dag par 'das pa'i phyir gnas med pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-13: shes rab ni bden pa las nges par 'byung bas don dam pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-14: shes rab ni shin tu dul ba rnams kyi mi 'khrugs pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-15: shes rab ni ye shes kyi sgo rnams kyi snang ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-16: shes rab ni thams cad du rgyu ba ste mi zad pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-17: shes rab ni brten pa las 'jug pa mthong ba ste mi 'gal ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-19: nyon mongs pa'i bcings pa thams cad gcod pa'i phyir rnam par thar pa'i lam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-20: shes rab ni nyon mongs pa thams cad dang ma 'dres /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-23: sgrib par 'gyur pa'i chos thams cad dang lhan cig mi gnas pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-24: sems can thams cad kyi sems kyi spyod pa ji snyed par shes rab dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-25: ye shes kyi las kyang de snyed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-26: sems can thams cad kyi nyon mongs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-27: bag la nyal ji snyed par shes rab kyi spyod pa'i ye shes kyang de snyed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:200b-28: sems can thams cad kyi nyon mongs pa'i sgo ji snyed par shes rab la 'jug pa'i sgo'ang de snyed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-1: sangs rgyas rnams kyi shes rab ji snyed pa shes rab kyi gnas dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-3: de la byang chub sems dpas bslab par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-4: btsun pa sh'a radva ti'i bu /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-5: de ni byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi shes rab mi zad pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-6: shes rab mi zad pa 'dis byang chub sems dpa' rnams ye shes mi zad pa thob par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-7: shes rab mi zad pa bstan pa'i chos kyi le'u 'di bshad pa na byang chub sems dpa' sngon yongs su sbyang ba byas pa sum khri nyis stong gis mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob par gyur to; ;de nas byang chub sems dpa' blo gros mi zad pas tshe dang ldan pa sh'a radva ti'i bu la 'di skad ces smras so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-8: btsun pa sh'a radva ti'i bu /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-9: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi byams pa'ang mi zad pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-11: thug pa med pa'i phyir ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-12: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi byams pa ni thug pa med par shes par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-13: de dag gi byams pa nye bar sgrub pa yongs su chad pa med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-14: 'di ltar sems can gyis khams ji tsam pa de tsam du byang chub sems dpa' de'i byams pa'i sems bskyed pas khyab par byed do; ;btsun pa sh'a radva ti'i bu /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-17: nam mkha' 'dis gar yang ma khyab pa med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201a-18: btsun pa sh'a radva ti'i bu /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-0: de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa'i byams @201b pa 'dis gar ma khyab pa'i sems can de gang yang med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-3: sems can gyi khams ni tshad med de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-4: de la zad pa med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-5: de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa'i byams pa bsgom pa'ang tshad med de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-6: de la zad pa med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-7: 'di ltar nam mkha'i mi zad pas na sems can mi zad pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-8: sems can mi zad pas na byams pa mi zad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-9: de'i phyir skyes bu dam pa de dag gi byams pa mi zad pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-10: de skad ces smras pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-11: gnas brtan sh'a ri'i bus byang chub sems dpa' blo gros mi zad pa la 'di skad ces smras so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-13: sems can gyi khams 'di ji tsam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-14: blo gros mi zad pas smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-15: btsun pa sh'a radva ti'i bu /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-19: rlung gi khams ji snyed pa de bas kyang sems can gyi khams ches mang ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-23: blo gros mi zad pas smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-24: btsun pa sh'a radva ti'i bu /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-25: nus mod kyi rgyu chung ngus ni ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-26: btsun pa sh'a radva ti'i bu /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-29: shar phyogs kyi 'jig rten gyi khams gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-30: de bzhin du lho phyogs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:201b-31: de bzhin du nub phyogs dang; de bzhin du byang phyogs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202a-0: de bzhin du phyogs bcu kun tu phyogs re rer yang 'jig rten gyi khams gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed de dag thams cad rgya mtsho chen po chus yongs @202a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202a-1: su gang ba gcig tu gyur la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202a-2: sems can gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed dag 'dus te skra'i rtse mo brgyar gshags pa'i chas de las chu thigs pa gcig blangs la; de bzhin du gang na'ang sems can gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed dag 'dus te bskal pa gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed dag na skra'i rtse mo brgyar gshags pa'i chas chu las thigs pa gnyis blangs la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202a-4: bgrang ba 'di lta bus bskal pa gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed cing sems can gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed dag gis skra'i rtse mo brgyar gshags pa'i chas chu'i thigs pa re re blangs pas chu'i phung po de tsam zad par gyur kyang sems can gyi khams de ni thug pa'am zad pa gang yang med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202a-5: btsun pa sh'a radva ti'i bu /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202a-6: de ltar sems can gyi khams tshad med de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202a-7: de dag la byang chub sems dpa'i byams pas khyab par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202a-8: btsun pa sh'a radva ti'i bu /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202a-10: gang gi byams pa de lta bur sgom pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba tshad med pa de zad par nus sam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202a-14: byams pa sgom pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di 'dra ba zad par su 'dod pa de nam mkha' zad par 'dod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202a-15: byang chub sems dpa' gang gis byams pa mi zad pa 'di thos nas skrag par mi 'gyur na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-0: de dag kyang byams pa mi @202b zad par 'phags par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-1: blo gros mi zad pas smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-2: btsun pa sh'a radva ti'i bu /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-3: byams pa ni bdag srung zhing gzhan la phan par gnas pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-4: mchog tu rtsod pa med pa dang; gnod sems kyi tha ba'i skyon dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-6: 'khon du 'dzin pa thams cad rab tu 'joms pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-8: kun nas ldang ba dang bral ba ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-9: dad pa skyed cing sems can thams cad kyi 'khrul pa la nyes par mi lta'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-10: yongs su gdung ba med cing lus dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-11: sems bde ba skyed pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-12: gzhan gyi gnod par bya ba las shin tu 'das pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-13: nyes pa thams cad kyi 'jigs pa dang bral ba ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-14: 'phags pa'i lam dang mthun zhing gshe ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-15: sdang ba'i sems dang ldan pa'i sems can rnams dad par byed pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-16: g-yul thams cad las sgrol ba ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-18: mtshon cha 'chang ba ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-19: sems can thams cad rab tu thar bar bya ba la dga' ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-20: khong khro ba thams cad dang bral ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-23: thob kyis 'jal ba thams cad dang bral ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-26: tshigs su bcad pa thams cad 'byung bar byed pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-29: 'jig rten skyong ba thams cad kyis phyag byas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-30: rang gi gzi brjid kyi rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-31: mkhas pas rab tu bsngags pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-32: byis pa thams cad srung ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:202b-33: tshangs pa'i lam dang mthun pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-2: sems can thams cad thar pa'i lam gyi mchog theg pa thams cad yang dag par bsdus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-3: zang zing med pa'i bsod nams kyis bzung ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-4: bsod nams kyi tshogs thams cad bsags pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-5: rdzas las byung ba'i bsod nams bya ba'i dngos po thams cad kyis zil gyis nyin no ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-6: skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-7: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus brgyan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-9: ma tshang ba thams cad spangs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-11: mya ngan las 'das pa'i lam dang mthun pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-13: mi khom pa brgyad las 'das pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-14: chos kyi kun dga' la mos pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-16: longs spyong kyi dbang phyug la mngon par dga' ba med pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-17: sems can thams cad la sems snyoms pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-18: spyin pa'i spyor ba tha dad pa dang bral ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-20: bslab pa thams cad kyi sgo dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-21: tshul khrims 'chal ba thams cad yongs su skyob pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-22: bzod pa'i stobs ston pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-25: dregs pa thams cad dang bral ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-26: 'phags pa rnams 'jug pa'i bsam gtan dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-28: snyoms par 'jug pa'i rtsa ba mi 'khrugs pa'i brtson 'grus brtsams shing yang dag par sbyor ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203a-29: bya ba thams cad las yang dag par sgrol ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:203b-0: snyoms par @203b 'jug pas nyon mongs pa thams cad las nges par 'byung ba /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:267b-17: dam pa'i chos yongs su bzung bas ni sems can thams cad yongs su gzung bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:267b-18: de nas bcom ldan 'das la tshangs pa mi mjed kyi bdag pos 'di skad ces gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:267b-21: tshangs ris kyi lhar bcas pas bsam gtan gyi dga' ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:267b-24: gang na chos kyi rnam grangs 'di spyod pa de dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:267b-25: der chos kyi rnam grangs de mnyan pa'i slad du mchi'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:267b-26: de chos smra ba de dag gis ltas bzhis na 'dir tshangs pa mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs ris kyi lha rnams dang bcas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:267b-27: chos nyan pa'i phyir lhags so zhes 'tshal bar bgyi ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:267b-30: snang ba chen po mthong ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:267b-31: lha rdzas kyi dri ma nam pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-0: chos smra ba des chos kyi rnam grangs 'di la nges pa'i tshig @268a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-2: tshig gi mtshams sbyar bar tshig gi mtshams su mi bskyud cing drang bar spobs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-3: 'khor de dag thams cad kyang sems rnam par mi g-yeng bar chos la gus par yid la bgyid pas chos nyan pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-4: ltas bzhi po de dag gis mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pa tshangs ris kyi lha rnams dang lhan cig tu chos nyan du 'dir mchis par 'tshal bar bgyi'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-5: de nas bcom ldan 'das la bdud sdig can gyis 'di skad ces gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-7: chos kyi rnam grangs 'dis bdag gi stobs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-8: bzhon par bcas pa thams cad stobs chung bar bgyis so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-9: de ci'i slad du zhe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-11: byang chub sems dpa' gang gis chos kyi rnam grangs 'di thos pa ni de nyid kyis byang chub sems dpa' de bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu lung bstan pa lags te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-13: sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang na byang chub sems dpa' de gnas na de nyid sangs rgyas zhes bgyi'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-15: byang chub sems dpa' blo gros mi zad pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-16: chos kyi rnam grangs 'di'i gzi brjid kyi tshogs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-17: stobs bskyed pas bdag gi nga rgyal dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268a-19: dregs pa rnams bcom pas chos smra ba de dag bsrung ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268b-1: gang na chos kyi rnam grangs 'di spyod pa der sems bskyed pa'i bag tsam gyis kyang bar chad bgyid du mi mchi'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268b-2: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268b-4: dam pa'i chos yun ring du gnas par bya ba'i phyir chos kyi rnam grangs 'di khyod kyis zungs shig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268b-9: bdag gis chos kyi rnam grangs 'di gzung lags na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268b-10: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po dag ltar bdag gis chos kyi rnam grangs rgyas par bgyid pa'i rngo mi thogs lags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268b-11: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268b-13: chos kyi rnam grangs 'di rgyas par rnam par dbye ba'i phyir snying las chung dur gyis shig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268b-14: 'khor 'di na gang dag chos kyi rnam grangs 'di phyogs bcur rgyas par byed pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268b-15: dam pa'i chos yongs su 'dzin pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dag tshogs shing 'khod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:268b-16: de nas 'khor de nas byang chub sems dpa' bye ba phrag bcus dam pa'i chos yongs su gzung ba'i phyir bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269a-0: bdag cag gis 'dus pa chen po'i le'u'i chos kyi rnam grangs 'di phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten du ma lus par rdzogs shing rgyas par @269a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269a-2: 'jig rten gyi khams mi mjed 'di na'ang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po byams pa dam pa'i chos yongs su gzung ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269a-3: dam pa'i chos bsrung ba'i slad du chos kyi rnam grangs 'di rgyas par bgyid de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269a-4: bcom ldan 'das yongs su mya ngan las 'das nas slad ma'i 'dus lnga brgya pa tham la chos kyi rnam grangs 'di byang chub sems dpa' gang dag gi rna lam du grag par 'gyur ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269a-8: ston pa de dag ni byang chub sems dpa' byams pa'i byin gyi rlabs su rig par bgyi'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269a-9: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis dam pa'i chos yongs su 'dzin pa byang chub sems dpa' de dag la bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269a-10: skyes bu dam pa dag; ji ltar khyod da ltar nga'i mdun na dam pa'i chos yongs su 'dzin par langs pa de bzhin du khyod sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed kyi spyan sngar dam pa'i chos yongs su 'dzin par langs pa legs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269a-12: de nas bcom ldan 'das la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po blo gros me zad pas 'di skad ces gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269a-14: bdag blo zhan pas bdag gis chos kyi rnam grangs 'dir don dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-0: yi ge yongs su rdzogs par ma bgyis pa lta na bcom ldan @269b 'das dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-1: mi zad pa'i chos dang ldan pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'di dag la bdag bzod pa gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-2: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-4: so so yang dag par rig pa sgrib pa med pa thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams la don dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-7: spobs pa rnams la 'khrul pa med do; ;'gog pa la'ang 'khrul pa med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-8: gang dag chos 'di lta bu dag rtogs par khong du chud pa'i skyes bu dam pa de dag ni yang dag pa'i don rnam par nges pa thob pa yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-10: khyod ni so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi'i dam pa'i mchog thob cing dbang rnyed ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-11: theg pa chen po 'di la gzhan gyi dring la mi 'jog cing rnam par nges pa'i dam pa'i mchog thob pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-13: sa 'di thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams la lus kyi 'khrul pa'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-15: sems kyi 'khrul pa gang yang med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-16: de dag thams cad ni ye shes sngon du 'gro ba'i lus dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-18: yid kyi las dang ldan pa yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-20: khyod ni sangs rgyas bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong mang pos chos bstan pa'i phyir rjes su dgongs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:269b-21: blo gros mi zad pa de lta bu rnams kyis khyod 'dra ba'i skyes bu dam pa rnams la shin tu bzod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-0: de nas bcom ldan 'das la tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' @270a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-3: chos kyi rnam grangs 'di'i ming ci lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-4: 'di ji lta bur gzung bar bgyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-5: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-7: de'i phyir khyod kyis chos kyi rnam grangs 'di blo gros mi zad pas bstan pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-10: yi ge mi zad pa bstan pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-12: blo gros mi zad pa'i le'u zhes bya bar yang zungs shig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-13: kun dga' bo khyod kyis 'dus pa chen po'i le'u'i chos kyi rnam grangs 'di gzung na de las chos la dran pa'i stobs kyi mthu bskyed pa 'bum 'gyur du thob par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-14: gzhan dag la'ang bstan na sems can thams cad la sangs rgyas kyi bya bas nye bar gnas par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-15: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-16: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs de dag thams cad dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-17: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po blo gros mi zad pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-18: gnas brtan sh'a radva ti'i bu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-20: thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor de dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-24: dri zar bcas pa'i 'jig rten yi rangs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-25: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270a-26: 'dus pa chen po'i le'u 'bum pa las blo gros mi zad pas bstan pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs so ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270b-0: @270b zhus chen gyi lo ts'a ba bande dharma t'a sh'i las zhus /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-060-004:270b-1: skad gsar bcas kyis kyang bcos te gtan la phab pa //
